sfer learning capability of 3D UX-Net\nwith AMOS2022 and demonstrates another improvement of $2.27\\%$ Dice (from 0.880\nto 0.900). The source code with our proposed model are available at\nhttps://github.com/MASILab/3DUX-Net.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2022 19:54:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Oct 2022 04:26:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2023 04:55:36 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 2 Mar 2023 03:58:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-03"}
