ess\nhas a dependence on the stellar mass progenitor. This fragmentation is made\npossible by the distribution of gas in the previous post-common envelope\nproto-planetary nebula as sculpted by the action of the jets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2022 20:16:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
